## Support to Analysis

- Simplify and summarize large data sets  
- Much more efficient than human-driven analysis

## Applicable to Real-World Intelligence

- Increased efficiency increases productivity  
- Allows analysts to tackle more problems  
- Intelligence analysis often runs under a time constraint  
- Better prepares decision-makers in a timely manner

## Limitations

- Policymakers may not trust reasoning  
- Possible mistakes that could have grave consequences in intelligence analysis issues
